{"tid":754872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[整理/轉] 重口，有關世界食人(Canniball)案件&討論","createTime":"2018-07-24T17:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T03:04:35.000Z","uid":186912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"180d9744ea6a6fda7a6792231ab35fa770f8bcee","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:59:39.000Z","msg":"前言---<br />\n自接觸到Hannabal後，比依個角色設定所吸引而開始對食人案件有性趣<br />\n所以想試下Search同整理一下世界食人各地有關食人嘅案件，唔知大家有冇性趣睇，畢竟都好重口下，唔係人人接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：樓豬 文 筆 極 差+第一次發post，同埋工作比較忙，可能up得比較慢，有咩不足請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下去文"},{"pid":"b8819df6681f1e728550f740617219c469170bc6","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>1). 戰鬥民族食人夫婦 (Russian cannibal couple)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/020009_4ee5cdc99208cadf4dc1103b744b8d64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F020009_4ee5cdc99208cadf4dc1103b744b8d64.jpg&h=d9aa6356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯人：Dmitry Bakshaev（夫），Natalia Baksheeva（婦）<br />\n國家：俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n於2017年，一修理道路工作人員拾獲一部手機，發現手機內有一名男性和同人類軀體自拍照片，然後報警逮捕依對夫婦。<br />\n<br />\n經調查後發現，依對夫婦應該早係<span style=\"color: red;\">18年前</span>已經開始殺人食用(應該係透過交友網站)，因有啲照片係拍攝於1999年12月29日，預計受害者超過30人。佢地會將<span style=\"color: red;\">人類遺體存放係雪箱同地下室，而且係殺人後會拎啲屍體出黎玩同埋影相/自拍。</span><br />\n而最近一位受害者係35歲嘅Elena Vashrusheva，疑因Natalia覺得Elena想姣佢老公，所以心生嫉妒就殺害同肢解左佢，殘肢被發現係佢地屋企附近。<br />\n<br />\n過程：殺人---&gt;保留屍體玩(影相/自拍)---&gt;肢解/剝皮後(影相/自拍)---&gt;食用<br />\n<br />\n事件當中，<span style=\"color: red;\">女性係主導者</span>，比較積極，並煽動同老公一齊殺人同食人。<br />\n<br />\n玩弄屍體方法（部分有圖，請慎開，因顧及到部分人唔敢睇，所以會加文字描述）：<br />\n<br />\n依張係最1999年12月28日所拍攝，佢地張一個被切斷嘅人頭同埋一大堆橙放係個大盤上做裝飾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747988d1506363019-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353406823.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentingreality.com%2Fforum%2Fattachments%2Ff237%2F747988d1506363019-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353406823.jpg&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7ff11d14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747988d1506363019-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353406823.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知係人嘅頭髮，定係假髮，被放置係工作台上<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747989d1506363020-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353359156.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentingreality.com%2Fforum%2Fattachments%2Ff237%2F747989d1506363020-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353359156.jpg&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d7aae603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747989d1506363020-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353359156.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n將一名男屍嘅手切落黎，再塞入男屍口中，並做成手舉中指動作<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747985d1506363017-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353177679.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentingreality.com%2Fforum%2Fattachments%2Ff237%2F747985d1506363017-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353177679.jpg&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c1a8b7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747985d1506363017-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353177679.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n依張都係切手再扮係&rsquo;Liu&rdquo;鼻屎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747984d1506363016-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353114206.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentingreality.com%2Fforum%2Fattachments%2Ff237%2F747984d1506363016-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353114206.jpg&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ad73ea01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/attachments/f237/747984d1506363016-russian-cannibal-couple-1506353114206.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n係佢地屋企附近地下所發現嘅人頭皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://s4.scoopwhoop.com/anj/jsj/4b8ac0ac-192e-4a49-8017-e0bad3dd3700.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.scoopwhoop.com%2Fanj%2Fjsj%2F4b8ac0ac-192e-4a49-8017-e0bad3dd3700.jpg&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=20e23e8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s4.scoopwhoop.com/anj/jsj/4b8ac0ac-192e-4a49-8017-e0bad3dd3700.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n照片來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/f237/russian-cannibal-couple-180536/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentingreality.com%2Fforum%2Ff237%2Frussian-cannibal-couple-180536%2F&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cbc47bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentingreality.com/forum/f237/russian-cannibal-couple-180536/</a><br />\n<br />\n部分人肉，佢地會醃製並保存係玻璃罐到得閒用黎送飯，雪櫃肉都重有唔少&quot;謎肉&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/4550298/inside-the-russian-cannibal-familys-house-of-horrors-where-they-killed-and-ate-30-people-lured-from-dating-sites/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fnews%2F4550298%2Finside-the-russian-cannibal-familys-house-of-horrors-where-they-killed-and-ate-30-people-lured-from-dating-sites%2F%23&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bdc0e264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/4550298/inside-the-russian-cannibal-familys-house-of-horrors-where-they-killed-and-ate-30-people-lured-from-dating-sites/#</a><br />\n<br />\n警方重發現在19塊人皮，不過搵唔到圖。<br />\n此外，Natalia重向咖啡館老闆表示可以向佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">提供餡餅</span>，想增加自己收入，但當問到係用問肉整時，佢就答: Whatever is around. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩老闆最後拒絕左<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得，雖然警方話預計有大約30個受害人，但實際可能更多，因為都由10幾年前開始殺同食人，部分證據同受害者都比佢地消滅/消化哂...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地做到咁出面(啲殘肢/人皮係屋企附近週圍掉)，點解都要過左18年先被發現呢...附近一定好鬼臭，點解會冇人報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e735e67583f3aeda320d2848d643bfe2f3c33d4","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩先發現標題串錯字，想請教一下有冇得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d8532f79021b71c67f39e8f101cedd0e81e8f8","tid":754872,"uid":9700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"強帖留名"},{"pid":"6c987bc6fd85a55a89fd78ec4cc91e6956db9388","tid":754872,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e735e67583f3aeda320d2848d643bfe2f3c33d4","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩先發現標題串錯字，想請教一下有冇得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"1989e3fa26920e076845379581938ee06f5fd0f2","tid":754872,"uid":88109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcbd646bd00b5b21d5624365348cf47686a23c2","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c987bc6fd85a55a89fd78ec4cc91e6956db9388","tid":754872,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e735e67583f3aeda320d2848d643bfe2f3c33d4","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩先發現標題串錯字，想請教一下有冇得改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"So9sad，感謝回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98254484d0a73e170d8578b3def7f175db1b7df","tid":754872,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"18f09a0225ce5b169dd828ef3947b5619310ac60","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"襯岩岩開始 開過個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e90d338f5caac67c390f797e4fbaeaa168db75c","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18f09a0225ce5b169dd828ef3947b5619310ac60","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"襯岩岩開始 開過個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"如果開新我依個Post有冇得dele? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c440e052efb391a89bdb56f653bd720108ef7879","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e90d338f5caac67c390f797e4fbaeaa168db75c","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18f09a0225ce5b169dd828ef3947b5619310ac60","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"襯岩岩開始 開過個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"如果開新我依個Post有冇得dele? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:36:30.000Z","msg":"冇呀 由佢沉當冇開過啦"},{"pid":"e5f5141b2dda0c3298a354db636b43b75bc8f4f2","tid":754872,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c98254484d0a73e170d8578b3def7f175db1b7df","tid":754872,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c225b8b10b6d5edf9f1fc739ec43336d3264b7","tid":754872,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eef7330461e27e9fa870f9b0d83d057b0d68f7","tid":754872,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"897193e36fa925d2adee657fc6748c9678adf655","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>2). The Cannibal Cafe 德國自願者食人事件</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/130751_aef9805e2f59c5bc717d71a59fa8076c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F130751_aef9805e2f59c5bc717d71a59fa8076c.jpg&h=24141da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯人：Armin Meiwes<br />\n國家：德國<br />\n<br />\n犯人Armin 一直好渴求人肉，佢2001年係The Cannibal Cafe到開post徵自願者比佢食用。<br />\n佢提出嘅條件係：約18-30歲左右體格良好嘅人。<br />\n意外地，竟然有好多人都有聯絡佢想做自願者...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時佢多收到唔少應徵，但當然有大部分都係fake嘅，一係就條件唔岩，最後佢睇中左Bernd Jurgen Brandes，並約左係聖誕節見面。<br />\n<br />\n整個過程發生係Armin屋企，全程Armin都有拍片。<br />\n首先，佢地啪啪啪左先(hehe)，因為食人係性癖之一，佢地係FF食人/被食時會性興奮。然後Armin比Bernd食左大約20粒安眠藥同飲酒黎減輕過程痛楚。<br />\nBernd床照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/sRWzCIn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FsRWzCIn&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=834ac223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/sRWzCIn</a><br />\n<br />\nArmin一開始先從佢最感性趣&mdash;Bernd嘅丁丁落手，本來想直接咬下條丁，但因為真係太難撕開，Armin只撕開到一半左右，就直接拎利器切左條丁拎去煮。<br />\n佢提取出Bernd嘅脂肪當油，加鹽，胡椒，葡萄酒同大蒜去煮，但一個唔小心煮燶左，完成入唔到口，只好拎去喂狗....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(未完)"},{"pid":"1f9a2ca7f2cb47e1a0eb5333bed4ffbdf77b4bec","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"當時，Bernd已經大量出血，Armin放佢入浴缸再加熱水，放血約3個鐘，自己就係到睇&quot;Star Trek&quot;(???)<br />\n事前，Armin一早為Bernd整左個地下屠房，3個鐘後佢發現Bernd竟然重未死，就直接刺喉了結左Bernd，搬左去屠房倒掛切肉。<br />\n<br />\n(慎點!!)<br />\n佢打開Bernd雙腳咁倒掛，頭部已經被斬，地下放左個大桶，然後由佢丁丁位開始剖開屍體，內臟直接掉入下面個大桶。<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/CgOp2W5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCgOp2W5&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3283d063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/CgOp2W5</a><br />\n完全將Bernd左右切開左2件<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/P7nxOFd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FP7nxOFd&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5f923c26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/P7nxOFd</a><br />\nBernd上半身軀體，被放係大木台準備食用<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/KUA1Nwf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FKUA1Nwf&d=oUSrE2MXGl2XARJbduhK4k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=186deb0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/KUA1Nwf</a><br />\n<br />\n自此10個月內，佢每日都用唔同方法去煮嘅人肉(約4x-5x磅，幾個報導嘅數字都有出入)，切出嘅肉就放係pizza盒內保存，並試圖將骨頭磨成麵粉，非常環保節儉，而內臟同牙齒就埋係花園。<br />\n<br />\n佢食完人肉嘅後感係：覺得似豬肉，但又有啲苦澀<br />\n<br />\n2002年12月，人肉差唔多食哂，佢再去徵求下一個自願者時，對方本來以為佢係講笑，點知發現佢黎真嘅，就馬上報警。警方係佢屋企發現到重剩下嘅人肉，同埋佢錄製嘅殺人+食人影片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/132358_9f149370873d816d67b11f633bbfaaa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F132358_9f149370873d816d67b11f633bbfaaa8.jpg&h=889069d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2004年，由於Bernd係自願被食，所以只判左佢過失殺人，入獄8年半。到2005時控方上訴，拎判左改為無期徒刑，依家變左素食主意者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後補少少資料：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/132421_0bf4ccb1a89169c1fe260da66886c7eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F132421_0bf4ccb1a89169c1fe260da66886c7eb.jpg&h=5ba67dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/132427_a23d59d020457e3080204ad20e2e1341.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F132427_a23d59d020457e3080204ad20e2e1341.png&h=d9077aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Cannibal Cafe依個網應該係來自deep web，果到係一班[好想食人]，同[好想比人食]嘅人聚集，係到FF自己嘅慾望，如討論自己想點樣去煮食人肉，食人點樣提起佢地嘅性慾，佢地想食嘅咩人，同埋想點樣比人去食。<br />\n經依件事後，依個網已被警方打擊，開創人Perro Loco(非真名)比警察拉過一次，然後佢又再開多個新web: Dolcett Girls(唔太確定個名岩唔岩)，因為可能同deep web有關，我都唔敢再搵落去啦。"},{"pid":"9e7932148819571dc7089725dd38774b9747eb15","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c440e052efb391a89bdb56f653bd720108ef7879","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e90d338f5caac67c390f797e4fbaeaa168db75c","tid":754872,"uid":186912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18f09a0225ce5b169dd828ef3947b5619310ac60","tid":754872,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"襯岩岩開始 開過個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"如果開新我依個Post有冇得dele? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:36:30.000Z","msg":"冇呀 由佢沉當冇開過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"算啦我照係到up，廢事其他人見到有2個post混淆到佢地<br />\n唔想麻煩到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thx"},{"pid":"7e480d8b51a7c2ac370a5c33100f8716aa48e531","tid":754872,"uid":88386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"👍🏽當故仔睇"},{"pid":"5e1ceff6becc984809712f2be6cef459e8ca259a","tid":754872,"uid":183367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"高質"}]}